item.description: hello-world It wouldn’t be a tech project without this. I’m Alex and I enjoy messing around with pretty much anything to do with data and analytics. I currently work in business intelligence and hope to transition into a data science path. My core skillset is: SQL Python Tableau My work environment requires: Engagement with agile process Work with containers Delivery within CD and manual release frameworks Effective communication with team and stakeholders Task priorisation :octocat:
